text:
Producer,
Are you okay with taking the afternoon off today?

Yeah, that's fine.
Just make sure not to schedule anything. Take a note of it.

Seems like a friend from high school is coming over,
So I'm planning to meet up with them.

Oh, that sounds nice.
Enjoy it as if you're back in high school.

Haha, "enjoy it as if you're back in high school," huh?
Sounds like advice from an adult.

Don't, don't say it...!
I was just thinking that as I said it myself...!
